lead_paragraph: Nina Davis scored 14 points to help No. 4 Baylor rally from an early deficit and ensure at least a share of their sixth-straight Big 12 Conference regular season crown with a 63-52 win over Kansas State on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Davis Helps Baylor Win Share of Sixth-Straight Big 12 Crown
